bDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 04:10:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-overdue-results-set-show-steep-losses-amid-sectors-sales-slump-2025-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国散户投资者对股票的兴趣迅速下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-retail-investor-sours-quickly-stocks-2025-01-14/</link><description>日内交易员陆德龙对中国股市上涨的乐观情绪在今年第一周迅速消失，在北京刺激计划推动股市上涨的三个月后，他被迫抛售股票并计算损失。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 02:32:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-retail-investor-sours-quickly-stocks-2025-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国向争议浅滩派遣“巨轮”后菲律宾感到震惊</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-deployment-monster-ship-alarming-says-philippine-security-official-2025-01-14/</link><description>周二，在北京派遣其最大的海岸警卫队船只进入马尼拉海域后，菲律宾指责中国在有争议的南海浅滩恐吓其渔民，并将“非法存在”正常化。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 02:31:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-deployment-monster-ship-alarming-says-philippine-security-official-2025-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜在特朗普回归前发射短程导弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-fires-missile-off-east-coast-says-south-korea-military-2025-01-14/</link><description>韩国军方表示，朝鲜周二在东海岸发射了多枚短程弹道导弹，这标志着平壤在美国候任总统唐纳德·特朗普重返办公室几天前进行了最新的武力展示。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 00:57:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-fires-missile-off-east-coast-says-south-korea-military-2025-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，中国正在考虑将 TikTok US 出售给马斯克</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-mulls-potential-sale-tiktok-us-musk-bloomberg-news-reports-2025-01-14/</link><description>据彭博社周一报道，如果短视频应用程序无法避免即将实施的禁令，中国官员正在就将 TikTok 在美国的业务出售给亿万富翁埃隆·马斯克的潜在选择进行初步谈判。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 00:25:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-mulls-potential-sale-tiktok-us-musk-bloomberg-news-reports-2025-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>美国议员敦促拜登延长 TikTok 1 月 19 日禁令期限</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-lawmakers-urge-biden-extend-tiktok-jan-19-ban-deadline-2025-01-14/</link><description>两名民主党议员周一敦促国会和总统乔·拜登延长 1 月 19 日中国字节跳动出售 TikTok 美国资产的最后期限，否则将面临美国禁令。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 00:06:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-lawmakers-urge-biden-extend-tiktok-jan-19-ban-deadline-2025-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>2024 年全球电动汽车销量将创纪录增长 25%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/global-electric-vehicle-sales-up-25-record-2024-2025-01-14/</link><description>周二的数据显示，随着中国持续增长和欧洲企稳，12 月份连续第四个月销量创纪录，全电动和插电式混合动力汽车的全球销量去年增长了四分之一，达到超过 1700 万辆。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 00:05:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/global-electric-vehicle-sales-up-25-record-2024-2025-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>独家：特朗普有意聘请华盛顿贸易律师担任商务部重要的中国职位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/trump-eyes-washington-trade-lawyer-key-china-post-commerce-dept-2025-01-13/</link><description>据知情人士透露，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普正在考虑任命华盛顿贸易律师杰弗里·凯斯勒领导美国商务部工业与安全局（BIS），这是美中科技战中的一个关键职位。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 23:08:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/trump-eyes-washington-trade-lawyer-key-china-post-commerce-dept-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：美元走势并未减弱，美国收益率紧缩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2025-01-13/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 21:47:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>尽管危机持续，拜登仍捍卫外交政策记录</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-defends-foreign-policy-record-despite-ongoing-crises-2025-01-13/</link><description>即将卸任的总统乔·拜登周一试图提升自己的外交政策记录，并表示，尽管全球危机仍未解决，但美国的对手比他四年前上任时更弱。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 20:28:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-defends-foreign-policy-record-despite-ongoing-crises-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>飞利浦首席执行官预计今年中国销量低迷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/philips-ceo-sees-subdued-china-sales-this-year-2025-01-13/</link><description>飞利浦首席执行官罗伊·雅各布斯(Roy Jakobs)表示，由于中国政府的医疗保健反腐败努力损害了西方公司在中国的收入，他仍然预计今年中国的需求将低迷。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 18:55:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/philips-ceo-sees-subdued-china-sales-this-year-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥的谢因鲍姆制定了削减中国进口的计划，显然是对特朗普的认可</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexicos-sheinbaum-lays-out-roadmap-make-country-an-economic-powerhouse-2025-01-13/</link><description>墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆周一推出了一项旨在限制从中国进口的经济计划，这显然是对美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普及其关于墨西哥是中国商品进入美国的后门的指控的认可。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 17:53:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexicos-sheinbaum-lays-out-roadmap-make-country-an-economic-powerhouse-2025-01-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>